<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Introduction Request Approval</title>
    <style>
      /* Add your CSS styles here */
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        margin: auto;
      }
      h2 {
        color: #333333;
        margin-top: 0;
      }
      p {
        color: #666666;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        /* text-align: center; */
        color: #888888;
      }
      .italic {
        font-style: italic;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Hello <%= requestedName %>,</h2>
      <p>
        We are helping some of the upcoming stars in the Blume portfolio reach
        their best prospects where we perceive the pain to be real and
        meaningful to solve. In this regard, we're connecting you to <%=
        requestorCompanyName %>'s founder, <%= requestorName %>. Please find
        below a small blurb about <%= requestorCompanyName %>:
      </p>
      <p class="italic"><%= companyBlurb %></p>
      <p class="footer">Regards,<br />Blume Admin</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
